Package: nychex
Title: Tessellated Hex Maps for New York City Geographies
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
    person("Kieran", "Healy", , "kjhealy@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9114-981X"))
Description: Provides sf objects containing hexagonal tile maps for New York
    City administrative geographies. Each polygon in the source geography is
    represented by a single hexagonal tile, preserving the overall spatial
    layout of the city.
LazyData: true
LazyDataCompression: xz
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://kjhealy.github.io/nychex/,
    https://github.com/kjhealy/nychex
BugReports: https://github.com/kjhealy/nychex/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
